Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,以Precure之美丽灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,邪悪な心を打ち砕く！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,于此将邪恶之心粉碎！
